{#-
  Resume base template (T12.14).

  Output: Markdown. The downstream pipeline (T12.15/T12.16) feeds this
  through the ``markdown`` library and then WeasyPrint to produce PDF.

  Safety contract
  ---------------
  * Render with Jinja2 ``autoescape=True``. Worker-supplied fields
    such as ``name`` and ``summary`` ARE escaped.
  * ``{{ contact | safe }}`` intentionally disables escape because
    ``contact`` is pre-rendered multi-line markdown assembled by the
    caller (e.g. ``"123 Main St\nworker@example.com"``). Callers MUST
    sanitise ``contact`` before passing it in.
-#}
# {{ name }}

{% if contact -%}
{{ contact | safe }}
{% endif %}

## Summary
{{ summary }}

## Skills
{% for skill in skills %}- {{ skill }}
{% endfor %}

## Work history
{% for role in work_history %}
### {{ role.title }} — {{ role.employer }}
{{ role.dates }}

{{ role.description }}
{% endfor %}

{% if barriers_cleared -%}
## Cleared barriers
{% for b in barriers_cleared %}- {{ b }}
{% endfor %}
{%- endif %}
